'From Squeak 2.4c of May 10, 1999 on 9 June 1999 at 2:45:25 pm'!"Change Set:		ThreeChanges-diDate:			9 June 1999Author:			Dan IngallsMakes Object class newFrom: use basicNew instead of new.Contracts selectors to 35 characters in the find-method menu of the browser.Redefines SystemDictionary removeEmptyMessageCategories to share rather than duplicate existing code."!!Object methodsFor: 'copying' stamp: 'di 6/9/1999 14:44'!copySameFrom: otherObject	"Copy to myself all instance variables named the same in otherObject.	This ignores otherObject's control over its own inst vars."	| myInstVars otherInstVars match |	myInstVars _ self class allInstVarNames.	otherInstVars _ otherObject class allInstVarNames.	myInstVars doWithIndex: [:each :index |		(match _ otherInstVars indexOf: each) > 0 ifTrue:			[self instVarAt: index put: (otherObject instVarAt: match)]]! !!Object class methodsFor: 'instance creation' stamp: 'di 6/9/1999 14:27'!newFrom: aSimilarObject	"Create an object that has similar contents to aSimilarObject.	If the classes have any instance varaibles with the same names, copy them across.	If this is bad for a class, override this method."	^ self basicNew copySameFrom: aSimilarObject! !!SystemDictionary methodsFor: 'housekeeping' stamp: 'di 6/8/1999 15:47'!removeEmptyMessageCategories	"Smalltalk removeEmptyMessageCategories"	Smalltalk garbageCollect.	(ClassOrganizer allInstances copyWith: SystemOrganization) do:		[:org | org removeEmptyCategories]! !